Interface Dumper<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the data to dump
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MeetingDumper, MeetingRequestDumper

    public interface Dumper<T>
    A class which can be used to give string representation to data types. It encapsulates the way data is represented.
